					<h1 class="text-center">The Grid</h1>

					<p>Kraken uses a fluid, mobile-first grid system based on simple fractions&mdash;halves, thirds, and fourths. It includes offsets, grid nesting, and special classes for content choreography and image galleries.</p>

					<h2 class="text-center">The Base Grid</h2>

				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="grid-third"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-third</div></div>
				<div class="grid-two-thirds"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-two-thirds</div></div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="grid-fourth"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-fourth</div></div>
				<div class="grid-three-fourths"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-three-fourths</div></div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="grid-half"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-half</div></div>
				<div class="grid-half"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-half</div></div>
			</div>

			<div class="row">
				<div class="grid-full"><div class="hero hero-condensed">.grid-full</div></div>
			</div>

